msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.dt.round"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:1
msgid "Perform round operation on the data to the specified `freq`."
msgstr "对数据执行指定 `freq` 的四舍五入操作。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:3
msgid ""
"The frequency level to round the index to. Must be a fixed frequency like"
" 'S' (second) not 'ME' (month end). See :ref:`frequency aliases "
"<timeseries.offset_aliases>` for a list of possible `freq` values."
msgstr ""
"要将索引四舍五入到的频率级别。必须是像 'S'（秒）这样的固定频率，而不是 '"
"ME'（月末）。有关可能的 `freq` 值列表，请参见 :ref:`频率别名 <timeseries."
"offset_aliases>`。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:8
msgid ""
"Only relevant for DatetimeIndex:  - 'infer' will attempt to infer fall "
"dst-transition hours based on   order - bool-ndarray where True signifies"
" a DST time, False designates   a non-DST time (note that this flag is "
"only applicable for   ambiguous times) - 'NaT' will return NaT where "
"there are ambiguous times - 'raise' will raise an AmbiguousTimeError if "
"there are ambiguous   times."
msgstr ""
"仅对 DatetimeIndex 有意义：  - 'infer' 会尝试根据顺序推断秋季夏令时转换"
"时间 - 布尔型数组，True 表示夏令时时间，False 表示非夏令时时间（注意此"
"标志仅适用于模糊时间） - 'NaT' 在存在模糊时间时返回 NaT - 'raise' 在存在"
"模糊时间时引发 AmbiguousTimeError。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:8
msgid "Only relevant for DatetimeIndex:"
msgstr "仅对 DatetimeIndex 有效："

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:10
msgid "'infer' will attempt to infer fall dst-transition hours based on order"
msgstr "'infer' 将根据顺序尝试推断夏令时转换时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:12
msgid ""
"bool-ndarray where True signifies a DST time, False designates a non-DST "
"time (note that this flag is only applicable for ambiguous times)"
msgstr ""
"bool-ndarray，其中 True 表示夏令时，False 表示非夏令时（注意此标志仅适用"
"于时间歧义）"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:15
msgid "'NaT' will return NaT where there are ambiguous times"
msgstr "'NaT' 在时间歧义处返回 NaT"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:16
msgid "'raise' will raise an AmbiguousTimeError if there are ambiguous times."
msgstr "'raise' 在存在时间歧义时抛出 AmbiguousTimeError。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:19
msgid ""
"A nonexistent time does not exist in a particular timezone where clocks "
"moved forward due to DST.  - 'shift_forward' will shift the nonexistent "
"time forward to the   closest existing time - 'shift_backward' will shift"
" the nonexistent time backward to the   closest existing time - 'NaT' "
"will return NaT where there are nonexistent times - timedelta objects "
"will shift nonexistent times by the timedelta - 'raise' will raise an "
"NonExistentTimeError if there are   nonexistent times."
msgstr ""
"在某些时区中由于夏令时导致时钟向前调整，某些时间不存在。  - 'shift_"
"forward' 会将不存在的时间向前移动到最近的现有时间 - 'shift_backward' 会将"
"不存在的时间向后移动到最近的现有时间 - 'NaT' 在存在不存在的时间时返回 NaT"
" - timedelta 对象会按 timedelta 移动不存在的时间 - 'raise' 在存在不存在的"
"时间时引发 NonExistentTimeError。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:19
msgid ""
"A nonexistent time does not exist in a particular timezone where clocks "
"moved forward due to DST."
msgstr "不存在的时间是指在特定时区中由于夏令时导致时钟向前移动而不存在的时间。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:22
msgid ""
"'shift_forward' will shift the nonexistent time forward to the closest "
"existing time"
msgstr "'shift_forward' 将不存在的时间向前移动到最近的现有时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:24
msgid ""
"'shift_backward' will shift the nonexistent time backward to the closest "
"existing time"
msgstr "'shift_backward' 将不存在的时间向后移动到最近的现有时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:26
msgid "'NaT' will return NaT where there are nonexistent times"
msgstr "'NaT' 在不存在时间处返回 NaT"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:27
msgid "timedelta objects will shift nonexistent times by the timedelta"
msgstr "timedelta 对象将按 timedelta 移位不存在的时间"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:28
msgid "'raise' will raise an NonExistentTimeError if there are nonexistent times."
msgstr "'raise' 在存在不存在时间时抛出 NonExistentTimeError。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:32
msgid ""
"Index of the same type for a DatetimeIndex or TimedeltaIndex, or a Series"
" with the same index for a Series."
msgstr ""
"对于 DatetimeIndex 或 TimedeltaIndex 返回相同类型的索引，对于 Series 返回"
"具有相同索引的 Series。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:39
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:40
msgid ""
"If the timestamps have a timezone, rounding will take place relative to "
"the local (\"wall\") time and re-localized to the same timezone. When "
"rounding near daylight savings time, use ``nonexistent`` and "
"``ambiguous`` to control the re-localization behavior."
msgstr ""
"如果时间戳具有时区，则四舍五入将相对于本地（“墙上”）时间进行，并重新"
"本地化到相同时区。在夏令时附近进行四舍五入时，使用 ``nonexistent`` 和 ``"
"ambiguous`` 来控制重新本地化行为。"

