msgid "**Series**"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:68
msgid ""
"When rounding near a daylight savings time transition, use ``ambiguous`` "
"or ``nonexistent`` to control how the timestamp should be re-localized."
msgstr ""
"在夏令时转换时间附近进行四舍五入时，使用 ``ambiguous`` 或 ``nonexistent``"
" 控制时间戳的重新本地化方式。"

